(7, 51, '他**便**利店买东西。', NULL, '{"type":"polyphonic","options":["biàn","pián"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"「便利」读 biàn lì，表示方便。"}'::jsonb),
(7, 52, '这首**乐**曲听起来让人心旷神怡。', NULL, '{"type":"polyphonic","options":["yuè","lè"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"「乐曲」读 yuè qǔ，指音乐作品。"}'::jsonb),
(7, 53, '他做事总是**磨**磨蹭蹭，半天也完不成一件。', NULL, '{"type":"polyphonic","options":["mó","mò"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"「磨磨蹭蹭」读 mó，表示拖延磨蹭。"}'::jsonb),
(7, 54, '这家小**磨**坊磨出来的豆腐特别香。', NULL, '{"type":"polyphonic","options":["mó","mò"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"「磨坊」读 mò fáng，指磨面粉的作坊。"}'::jsonb),
(7, 55, '他性格倔**强**，从不轻易向人低头。', NULL, '{"type":"polyphonic","options":["qiáng","qiǎng","jiàng"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"「倔强」读 jué jiàng，表示固执不屈。"}'::jsonb),
